---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
const today = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' });
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Des Moines Junk Removal" description="Privacy policy for Des Moines Junk Removal. How we collect, use, and protect your information." path="/privacy/">

<section style="padding-top:3rem;">
  <Breadcrumb trail={[{ name: "Home", href: "/" }, { name: "Privacy Policy" }]} />
  <div class="container legal-content">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="note">This is a starting template. For final legal review, consult a licensed attorney in Iowa.</p>
    <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> {today}</p>

    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you submit a quote form or contact us, we collect your name, phone number, email address, city, and details about your hauling job. We also collect basic analytics data (pages visited, device type, referrer) through Google Analytics if installed.</p>

    <h2>How We Use It</h2>
    <p>We use your contact info to respond to your quote request, schedule your pickup, and follow up after service. Analytics data helps us improve the website.</p>

    <h2>Who We Share It With</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your information. We share data only with service providers we use to operate the business, such as our form delivery service and Google Analytics. We never share your details with other hauling companies, marketing lists, or third parties.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can request deletion of your information at any time by emailing <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use minimal cookies, primarily for analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings without affecting how the site works.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a> or call <a href={`tel:${site.phoneE164}`}>{site.phone}</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
